<template>
    <el-container>
        <el-main style="margin: auto;width:100%">
            <el-table
                    :data="tableData"
                    style="width: 100%"
                    :default-sort = "{prop: 'date', order: 'descending'}"
            >
                <el-table-column
                        prop="date"
                        label="日期"
                        sortable
                        width="180">
                </el-table-column>
                <el-table-column
                        prop="name"
                        label="姓名"
                        sortable
                        width="180">
                </el-table-column>
                <el-table-column
                        prop="address"
                        label="地址"
                        :formatter="formatter">
                </el-table-column>
            </el-table>
        </el-main>
        <el-footer style="margin: auto">
            <el-container>
                <el-rate style="width:100%;"
                         v-model="value2"
                         :colors="colors">
                </el-rate>
            </el-container>
        </el-footer>
    </el-container>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: "charts",
        data() {
            return {
                value1: null,
                value2: null,
                colors: ['#99A9BF', '#F7BA2A', '#FF9900'],  // 等同于 { 2: '#99A9BF', 4: { value: '#F7BA2A', excluded: true }, 5: '#FF9900' }
                tableData: [{
                    date: '2020-05-02',
                    name: '张翛然',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1518 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-04',
                    name: '朱行星',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1517 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-01',
                    name: '张有坤',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1519 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-05',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-06',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-07',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-08',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-09',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-10',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }, {
                    date: '2020-05-03',
                    name: '赖永炫',
                    address: '厦门市思明区海韵路 1516 号'
                }]
            }
        },
        methods: {
            formatter(row) {
                return row.address;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
